Class LiteralBodyBuilder

    BodyBuilder

    public class LiteralBodyBuilder
extends AbstractBodyBuilder
    An implementation of BodyBuilder that supports creating the SOAP body for Webservices based upon a WSDL with Literal style.
    Author:
    Stuart Owen, Stian Soiland-Reyes
